title: Andy Warstar - 03/29/07 Nim FM 102.3 - Complete Show
description:
The Andy Warstar Radio Hour No. 1, featuring Andy Warstar & the music of the

Warstars. In Australia, it&#039;s not illegal to practice &#039;plug-ola&#039;... You can have

your own show and promote yourself. Pretty cool, huh? And sometimes, if the DJ who

works at the community radio station doesn&#039;t pay his friend&#039;s membership dues like

he says he&#039;s gonna, as a favor, well... you might just end up doing your own radio

show for a whole month at some community radio station out in B.F.E. without

anybody from the station realizing it! At least that&#039;s what happened with Andy.
